OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FThis evening
OL,6,Fwill be dry with late brightness in
OL,7,Fplace. The rest of the night will
OL,8,Fremain dry with clear spells,
OL,9,Fespecially in the east. .
OL,10,
OL,11,CTuesday:FGood sunny spells between
OL,12,Fpatchy amounts of cloud. Most places
OL,13,Fwill remain dry, but the odd light
OL,14,Fpassing shower possible in the west.
OL,15,
OL,16,COutlook for Wednesday to Friday:FMainly
OL,17,Fdry with very warm sunshine on
OL,18,FWednesday and Thursday. Cloudier later
OL,19,FThursday into Friday with the risk of
OL,20,Fa few showers.
